<br>
This last month I have had to deal with some of THE rudest and immature people I have come in contact with.. all over ONE real woman.  Before you start tossing stones at her..<br>
<br>
In my EQ playing career.. almost 4 years now, I have been stalked, abused verbally, and harassed in what is primarily a male-dominated society... the constant flirtation over my character.. the *BITCH* when I refuse advances.. etc.  It gets on my nerves.<br>
<br>
So we took someone into the guild that was having the SAME problems I have had all along.. old story.  She was *dating* someone in the game... he took it too seriously.. she backed off... he freaks out.  We took her and her RL boyfriend into the guild and did so quietly.. she said nothing about anything to us.. and WHAMMO!  the tells started.<br>
<br>
It seems her old guild is out to ruin her name... just because the guild leader was spurnned.  Sheeeesh.  It has gone WAY too far and ending in a petition so far today because I am sick of the constant tells... but I thought since there was an excellent post about RL feelings on here that I would extend that... <br>
<br>
Here was this mornings conversation.. notice where he admits several times that they are actively policeing anyone who comes in contact with her... /rude  And that they will ban any members who talks to her.. which of course excludes themselves and anyone who wishes to harass those around her.<br>
<br>
I finally went to their website and asked them to leave us alone... because *chatting* was getting nowhere.  And the new round of crap began =P<br>
<br>
Sure this is a game.. but people DO get hurt.. AND there are freaks on here too.<br>
<br>
