Poyson M`brace   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=kallisiafv>Kallisia FV</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.rpgicons.com/images/icons/lufia2/npcs/hilda/wound.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>The girl of Faerie</span><br>  Posts: 46<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(5/20/03 1:01 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm49.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=39.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.natsume.com/games/LUF_tlr/graphics/milka.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Stalking on EQ</span><hr size=1> I have had to deal with this kind of thing before.  Not exactly this advanced though.  <br>
